{"tid":533913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"考評局不建議用塗改帶/液改答案","createTime":"2018-01-19T09:43:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-22T15:58:32.000Z","uid":28366,"like":15,"dislike":76,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"867dd5854eb2c23ec3ffdb6d98e2ab2b2fe4689e","tid":533913,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T09:43:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/19/174016_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F19%2F174016_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=57aab188&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">中學文憑試（DSE）將於3月至5月舉行，考評局建議考生作答選擇題除了可用HB鉛筆，用原子筆亦可。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/19/174020_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F19%2F174020_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=727353fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">溫德榮提醒考生，應考時謹記帶備准考證和身份證，或其他有效身份證明文件，亦要把考生條碼貼在答卷的適當位置。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/19/174022_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F19%2F174022_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=792d74fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">負責閱卷的評核發展部經理徐力航亦提醒考生字體要清晰，特別中文字，如果未能辨別，就未能給予分數。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/19/174153_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F19%2F174153_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=076780af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">溫德榮建議，考生筆試作答時，以塗改帶或塗改液或會至紙張凹凸不平，影響掃描清晰度，建議以筆劃走錯的內容會更好。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/19/174233_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F19%2F174233_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=be248d44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中學文憑試（DSE）將於3月至5月舉行，考評局評核發展部總經理溫德榮建議考生，作答選擇題除了可用HB鉛筆，用原子筆亦可，「如果改答案嗰時，一定要圈好正確答案，如果唔係就當重複作答，畀唔到分」。考筆試時，塗改帶或塗改液可能導致至紙張凹凸不平，影響掃描清晰度，建議以筆劃走欲刪改的內容。<br />\n<br />\n溫德榮提醒考生，應考時謹記帶備准考證和身份證，或其他有效身份證明文件，亦要把考生條碼貼在答卷的適當位置。過往有考生沒有貼好條碼，或將答案寫在答卷邊界外，影響評核中心掃描機運作，須人手處理。<br />\n<br />\n溫又指，有考生在考場內拍照，或把考生條碼等放上網，都屬違規。溫指網上沒有秘密，局方必定跟進和懲處。他重申，考生有責任遵守《考生手冊》，若違犯將有相應處分，最嚴重或至考卷不予評閱。有負責閱卷的評核發展部經理徐力航亦提醒考生字體要清晰，特別是中文字，如果未能辨別，也未能給予分數。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180119/57725134\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180119%2F57725134&d=O%2FDIUHGNus3%2BZXxg%2BPUTdZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=47c4eaea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180119%2F57725134&h=f6ae1ab1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180119/57725134</a>"},{"pid":"875ad3b37a96898402315d9fc3f8806352148dab","tid":533913,"uid":130122,"like":100,"dislike":3,"score":97,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T09:45:20.000Z","msg":"評核發展部經理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽都未聽過"},{"pid":"ba4659750458233bf2137e99fae3a61185d0e971","tid":533913,"uid":115888,"like":146,"dislike":10,"score":136,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T09:47:39.000Z","msg":"刪到花囇改卷個個更唔想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bc4f037db9a5d9cd5de5973037b402ea19344e0","tid":533913,"uid":62274,"like":224,"dislike":1,"score":223,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T09:48:04.000Z","msg":"我學校不嬲都話考公開試唔好用塗改液<br />\n一嚟會scan唔到<br />\n二嚟會慢咗啦<br />\n所以不嬲都直接就咁畫走個答案算"},{"pid":"94fd3dd9bf8490ee2ee68222cbbae6c5bb58bc67